'''Mastigophorous''' was a clan of [[Drall/Legends|Drall]] living on the planet [[Drall (planet)|Drall]] at the time of the [[Corellian Crisis|First Corellian Insurrection]]. As [[Marcha]] was the oldest [[Gender/Legends|female]] in the clan, she became its [[Duchess/Legends|Duchess]].

